regen.absent_element: differentiation between busy line or network issue upon call failure
regen.new_specification: The system shall provide specific notifications to the driver to indicate whether the call failure is due to a busy line or a network issue.

regen.absent_element: indication of busy line or network issues upon failed call connection
regen.new_specification: If the system is not able to connect the call, the driver should be informed with specific indications if the failure is due to a busy line or network issues.

regen.absent_element: Specific indications of the reason for the call failure (busy line or network issues)
regen.new_specification: If the system fails to connect the call, the driver should be provided with audible and visual indications specifying whether the failure was due to a busy line or network issues.

label: This shall also indicate if the called party was busy or if the network could not connect the call.
absence: specific indication of unsuccessful connect: busy or network error
